{"tid":39004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兌現川普承諾？IBM宣布將釋出2萬5000個職缺","createTime":"2016-12-14T09:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T11:53:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"601446651fd5b63c03b8de5adcbf4751156047ca","tid":39004,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"兌現川普承諾？IBM宣布將釋出2萬5000個職缺<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-14<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1916717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1916717&d=%2F3wwz22z6HyrIHDyHV%2BVdQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b4e5ec5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1916717&h=dfd22b2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1916717</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpnXNt7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpnXNt7C.jpg&h=e7a80f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIBM執行長羅梅蒂（Virginia Rometty）。（彭博社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國共和黨準總統川普在競選期間，不斷以「美國優先」為號召，誓言要將工作機會留在美國本土，沒想到還沒就任，科技大廠IBM已經承諾，未來將在美國雇用2萬5000名員工。<br />\n<br />\n川普當選後積極與各方人士會面，日前先是獲得日本軟銀社長孫正義500億美金的投資承諾，預估可創造5萬個工作機會。而在科技業大老準備與川普會面前夕，IBM宣布將在美國釋出大量職缺。<br />\n<br />\nIBM執行長羅梅帝（Virginia Rometty）表示，「我們隨時可以提供上千個職缺，預計在4年內於美國僱用2萬5000名專業人士。」"},{"pid":"dbed2e21294813e3bf79d00ebf65fb235681f4fd","tid":39004,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f0187f399c6e46c14962f4e97f91fc6940c9ad","tid":39004,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"得個講字，你下年唔炒人先算LA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd5c4aa36049e75509af805e8cd5e63ae9e4156","tid":39004,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"IBM仲有係美國生產乜野"},{"pid":"4b05c5145a7def389e2775132e71092c2b6b465b","tid":39004,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad42fc77b19a34cff8fac32be274f125b3addcb","tid":39004,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IBM仲有係美國生產乜野</blockquote><br />\n使撚生產咩<br />\n做 system 發到豬頭丙咁"},{"pid":"2bcc14a7d0f095fe8208f00b179df97c213bf07c","tid":39004,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"買返thinkpad黎做啦"}]}